tafsir[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,"Si leydi dimmbaama dimmbagol cattungol baɗatngol ñande darnga."
  99,2,"Leydi ndi yaltini ko wonnoo e reedu mum ummaade maayɓe mum e ko nanndi heen."
  99,3,"Neɗɗo na wi*a hombo haawa: Hol ko woni fiyaaku ndi leydi ndillatndi polwotoondi."
  99,4,"E oon ñalawma mawɗa leydi ndi habra ko waɗano e mayri foti ko ko laba wolla ko boni."
  99,5,"Sabu ko Alla anndini ndi O yamiri ndi."
  99,6,"E oon ñalngu mawɗa mbo leydi ndi dimmmboto yimɓe njalta ummaade e nokku haasboore pelle pelle ngam ɓe ceedo golle mum en ɗe ɓe mbaɗno ka aduna."
  99,7,"Kala mo golli fotde gabbel jarra e golle moƴƴe e ɗiggere ma o taw ɗe yeeso makko."
  99,8,"Kala mo golli fotde ñuungel jarra e golle moƴƴe e ɗiggere ma o taw ɗe yeeso makko."
